---
import InfoGensoedCard from "../../components/InfoGensoedCard.astro";
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Info Gensoed"
  addClass="bg-[url('/images/patterns/batik.svg')] bg-size text-dark-base"
>
  <section id="hero" class="pb-16 pt-28 section-padding-x lg:min-h-screen">
    <div class="container max-w-screen-xl">
      <div class="w-full flex flex-col gap-4">
        <article class="text-center">
          <h1
            class="sub-header-font-size font-heading"
            data-aos="slide-down"
            data-aos-duration="400"
            data-aos-delay=""
            data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
            data-aos-offset="0"
            data-aos-once="true"
          >
            Info Gensoed
          </h1>
        </article>
        <div class="flex gap-4 md:gap-8 justify-center">
          <div
            class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:gap-8 w-full md:items-end lg:flex-row lg:items-start lg:justify-end"
          >
            <InfoGensoedCard
              title="Twibbon"
              img="/images/icons/general/twibbon.webp"
              href="/coming-soon"
              extraClass="animate-downUp"
            />
            <InfoGensoedCard
              title="Dresscode"
              img="/images/icons/general/dresscode.webp"
              href="/coming-soon"
              extraClass="animate-downUp lg:mt-12 lg:animate-upDown"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex flex-col gap-4 pt-12 md:gap-8 w-full lg:flex-row lg:pt-0"
          >
            <InfoGensoedCard
              title="Perbekalan"
              img="/images/icons/general/equipment.webp"
              href="/coming-soon"
              extraClass="animate-upDown lg:animate-downUp"
            />
            <InfoGensoedCard
              title="Lainnya"
              img="/images/icons/general/other.webp"
              href="/coming-soon"
              extraClass="animate-upDown lg:mt-12"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <p
          class="text-justify md:text-center normal-font-size animate-fade-up animate-once animate-duration-[600ms] animate-ease-out"
        >
          Hai Sobat Gensoed! laman ini berisi informasi terkait twibbon,
          dresscode, dan perlengkapan yang dibutuhkan selama rangkaian acara S3
          berlangsung yaa. Yuk dicek kembali agar tidak ketinggalan info terkait
          Soedirman Student Summit!ðŸ¦‹
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .bg-size {
    background-size: 128px;
  }
</style>
